{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_02",
  "title": "星見編2章27話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（レッスンの合間の休憩時間）\n（今日も月のテンペストのメンバーは賑やかだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s break time in between lessons.)\n(And today‚ the members of Moon Tempest are in high spirits as usual.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ！\n……できた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew!\nI did it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.108344634373983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "よくもまあ、そんな体勢を維持していられますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I am most impressed that you can maintain such a posture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.491700569788616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのは得意なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is one of my special skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.741700569788616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "バレエやダンスを習っていた訳でもないのに……\n……負けませんわよ！　――ほっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you’ve never trained in ballet and dance…\nYou won’t outshine me! Umph!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.108367236455287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そう言えばすずにゃんってさー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Suzu-nyan‚ I have a question.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.775033903121955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n……ぎにゃっ！？　アタタタタ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nEep?! Owww.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.726712004343668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 566.6666666666594,
          "startTime": 27.726712004343668
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いったいなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.060045337677007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "確か、麻奈ちゃんのこと好きなんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You love Mana‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.39040813446046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんって……\nあなた、長瀬麻奈様のことを言っていますの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By Mana…\nDo you mean Goddess Mana Nagase?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.69190462430321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "かの伝説のアイドルに\nやっと芽衣も興味を持ったのですわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You finally took an interest\nin that legendary idol‚ I see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.29190462430322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　うん、まあ、そんなとこ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Yeah‚ well‚ I guess so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.458571290969886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "よろしいですわ！\n私が長瀬麻奈様の全てを教えてあげましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very good!\nThen I shall tell you everything there is to know about Goddess Mana Nagase!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.03682533899947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "私、芽衣を立派な麻奈様ファンに\n仕立て上げてみせましてよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ I shall turn you into an excellent fan\nof Goddess Mana!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.38464130423537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.45985686642003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.55985686642005
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 63.89319019975337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……お風呂、上がったけど\n次は誰が入る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… I’m done with my bath.\nWho’s going next?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.89319019975333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 64.72652353308668
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それでは私が入らせていただきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I shall take my bath next.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.59319019975334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえすず\n最近、芽衣はどうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzu‚\nwhat’s been going on with Mei lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.70985677105256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "へ？\nどう……と言いますと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha?\nWhat do you mean exactly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.24319010438589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら……急にお姉ちゃんのことを\n気にし始めたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ she’s suddenly taken an interest\nin my big sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.20985677105254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。もちろん順調に\n麻奈様ファンとして育て上げていますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why‚ yes. And naturally‚ in time‚\nI shall turn her into a Goddess Mana fan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.615752481044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、最近芽衣ちゃん、毎晩フラッと\n出かけているみたいなんです。今日も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That reminds me‚ every evening lately‚ Mei\nseems to be going out somewhere. She did that tonight‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.24908581437737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "毎晩？\nコンビニに買い物とかかなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every evening?\nMaybe she’s going shopping at a convenience store?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.38241914771068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、夜中に女の子一人で\n出歩くものではないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I don’t think it’s a good idea for a girl\nto go out alone at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6824191477107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 106.58241914771072
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 106.88241914771072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そんな四人の会話が、ちょうど偶然）\n（廊下を通りかかった俺の耳に入ってきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As the four girls are talking‚ I happen to catch)\n(their conversation as I’m walking down the hall.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.58241914771072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも芽衣の外出を気にし始めたか\nうーん……やっぱりマズいよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone seems to wonder why Mei keeps going out.\nOh dear… This can’t be good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.71575248104408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 121.18241914771068
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 121.18241914771068
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.51575248104407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "へっへーん、じゃあ\n芽衣はオイシイこのカドっこをゲットー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee-hee! Well‚\nMei’s gonna get this juicy corner!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.44908581437744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 129.0157524810441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "ああああー！　私の白がっ！！\n黒く、塗りつぶされていくぅ……",
      "translations": {
